e been hard at work publishing research in academic journals as well as presenting their research at various conferences around the country and the world  Speakers Over the past academic year  our cadets were fortunate enough to hear from several speakers both from academia and business  Cadet Research The VMI Undergraduate Research Initiative  URI  was established by directive of the Dean of Faculty to more fully integrate student scholarly inquiry into the VMI experience  The Cadet Investment Group The Cadet Investment Group  CIG  was founded in 1986 by the VMI Foundation  The group s mission is to learn about investing  To do this  members serve as investment analysts and portfolio managers  Cadet Internships In the summer of 2009  five cadets participated in the inaugural summer of the department s  internship for credit  program  SBD and ODE Activity The Sigma Beta Delta  the Honor Society for Business and Omicron Delta Economics Honor Society were quite active this past year thanks to the leadership provided by Cadets Thompson and Johnston  Cadet Awards The Annual ODE Banquet to honor our top cadets was held on April 8th  Alumni Survey Calling all members of the Classes of 1994 and 2004  Stay Connected to ECBU  Please let us know what you ve been up to by emailing us at ECBUnewsletter vmi edu  If you are interested in hosting a field trip  accepting an intern  speaking to our cadets or helping out in any way at all  just let us know  Even if you have nothing to report  send an email to let us know that you want to be on our email list  Spring 2009 Newsletter AACSB Accreditation  Major Field Test in Business  Colonel Husted Retires  New Hire   Colonel Scarpaci  Faculty Scholarship  Speakers  Cadet Research  Cadet Investment Group  Cadet Internships  SBD and ODE Activity  Cadet Awards  Alumni Survey  Stay Connected  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   