cadets participated in the inaugural summer of the department s  internship for credit  program  SBD and ODE Activity The Sigma Beta Delta  the Honor Society for Business and Omicron Delta Economics Honor Society were quite active this past year thanks to the leadership provided by Cadets Thompson and Johnston  Cadet Awards The Annual ODE Banquet to honor our top cadets was held on April 8th  Alumni Survey Calling all members of the Classes of 1994 and 2004  Stay Connected to ECBU  Please let us know what you ve been up to by emailing us at ECBUnewsletter vmi edu  If you are interested in hosting a field trip  accepting an intern  speaking to our cadets or helping out in any way at all  just let us know  Even if you have nothing to report  send an email to let us know that you want to be on our email list  Spring 2009 Newsletter AACSB Accreditation  Major Field Test in Business  Colonel Husted Retires  New Hire   Colonel Scarpaci  Faculty Scholarship  Speakers  Cadet Research  Cadet Investment Group  Cadet Internships  SBD and ODE Activity  Cadet Awards  Alumni Survey  Stay Connected Information   Social Sciences Economics   Business Home Degrees   Programs Courses Economics Newsletter Spring 2015 Spring 2014 Spring 2013 Spring 2012 Spring 2011 Spring 2010 Spring 2009 Spring 2008 Spring 2007 Departmental Activities Policies   Forms About ECBU Faculty Open House Presentation Senior Exit Survey Alumni  97    07 survey Donna Potter Executive Secretary P   540  464 7234 F   540  464 7005 Virginia Military Institute 345 Scott Shipp Hall Lexington  VA  24450 Contact ECBU  Information   Social Sciences Economics   Business Home Degrees   Programs Courses Economics Newsletter Spring 2015 Spring 2014 Spring 2013 Spring 2012 Spring 2011 Spring 2010 Spring 2009 Spring 2008 Spring 2007 Departmental Activities Policies   Forms About ECBU Faculty Open House Presentation Senior Exit Survey Alumni  97    07 survey Donna Potter Executive Secretary P   540  464 7234 F   540  464 7005